Feature: Hotel Booking In Adactin Application

Scenario: Login Functionality

Given user Launch The Application

When user Enter The "softtester" In Username Field

And user Enter The "adc@123" In Password Field

Then user Click On The Login Button And It Navigates To The Search Hotel Page

Scenario: Search Hotel

When user Select The "London" In Location Field

And user Select The "Hotel Sunshine" In Hotels Field

And user Select The "Super Deluxe" In Room Type Field

And user Select The "10" In Location Field